PDF drawings are generated from IPE by: 
$ ipetoipe -pdf file.ipe

UML diagram was generated with AutoDia at first and then rearranged and
corrected manually.
Generation: autodia -i Berreman4x4.py -l python -o UML.dia
The file can be exported automatically with: dia -t pdf UML.dia
The reulsting PDF is then cropped with PDFCrop.

